<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[ABSTRACT This paper discusses guidelines and proposals aiming to support the debate on tax reform in Brazil. By doing so, it updates the diagnosis of the Brazilian tax structure and lists a few reform proposals to correct its distortions regarding taxation levied on goods and services, payroll and income.]]></p></abstract>
